. Regions discussed include the Mekong Delta in Vietnam, Moluccas, Central Kalimantan, West Sumatra and South Sulawesi in Indonesia and Tangail Region in Bangladesh.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAsia. 4aDevelopment. 4aEnvironment. 4aEnvironmental Sociology. 4aEthnology. 4aGlobalization. 4aNature. 4aPacific Asia. 4aRisk. 4aSoutheast Asia. 4aTropical Agriculture. 4aUncertainty. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aAsia.  aDevelopment.  aEnvironment.  aEnvironmental Sociology.  aEthnology.  aGlobalization.  aNature.  aPacific Asia.  aRisk.  aSoutheast Asia.  aTropical Agriculture.  aUncertainty.1 aAlam, Mahbub, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAntweiler, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAntweiler, Christoph, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBizard, Viola, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDeswandi, Rio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEhlert, Judith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEllen, Roy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFerse, Sebastian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlaser, Marion, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHARMS, ARNE, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHornidge, Anna-Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHornidge, Anna-Katharina, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMARTENS, SOFIE ELENA, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aReichel, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/